# Data-Type-Inference-App

## Backend
### First need install the necessary library

Run `pip install django pandas numpy django-cors-headers`

### Move direction to `BackEnd/DataInfer` folder

Run `python manage.py runserver ` to start Django Engine
Ensure the port is `8000`

## FrontEnd 

### Move direction to `FrontEnd/data-infer` folder

Run `npm install` first
Run `npm start` to start the react engine (Frontend web page)

## Note
To deal with the .xlsx files with multiple sheets, it will only process the first sheet of the file. Please ensure the first sheet is the correct excel 'table' format
